;
;   k has been calculated as follows:
;   - data form 225 nm to 532 nm (gap wavelength -25 nm) have been
;     obtained interpolating linearly each nm the data in the Sopra file
;   - data from 200 nm to 224 nm have been extrapolated lineraly
;   - data from 532 to 557 (gap wavelength) have been calculated assuming
;     a dependence k=real(A*sqrt(1/lambda -1/557))
;
;
